Leveraged GPT-3.5 and built a react library for seamless self-service registration forms and onboard customers to many internal apps. Integrated with ServiceNow for incident management and provided an intuitive UI using NextJS and Vercel AI SDK. Developed a real-time chat app with GunJS, incorporating on-device GenAI Gemini for language translation, during a Hackathon. Working with the business to write new capabilities, architect solutions, and provide KT sessions and demos to explain proposed solutions. Guiding and mentoring engineering teams on best practices. Built microservices using Quarkus, Mandrel, GraalVM, SpringBoot, and Docker for serverless functions, with HA enabled Active/Active state across clusters. Implemented Git Actions & Jenkins pipelines for CI/CD and integrated change control processes for production deployments. Established observability and telemetry for services. Being part of lean engineering team, built Optum Functions Platform (OFP), Optum's ﬁrst Serverless Platform (FPaaS) on Optum's private network. Created many customized features using Golang for self service and governance of the cluster. Achievements/Tasks
